      Product Description

      Muthoot Pappachan Group with a reputation shaped over decades with high-quality practices, total satisfaction and steady growth in the field of business, built on God-given values of trust, truth, transparency and tradition, has become one of the top business houses today by the grace of God.

      Muthoot Exim, the precious metal vertical of the Muthoot Pappachan Group, specialises in innovative products and offerings in the precious metal space. Customers have access to quality products that meet the highest standards at affordable prices.

      916 Purity BIS hallmarked jewellery

      Purity is an important factor when it comes to jewellery. Jewellery that is made of pure gold is free of any impurities and is more durable, valuable, and long-lasting. Gold jewellery that is BIS Hallmarked is even more valuable as it is certified by the Bureau of Indian Standards.

      999 Purity Coins

      999 purity coins are the highest quality coins available. They are made from pure gold or silver and are extremely valuable. These coins are usually minted by governments or banks and are highly sought after by collectors and investors alike.

      Positive Weight Tolerance

      Positive weight tolerance is the maximum amount of additional weight that an object can withstand during a test or measurement. It is commonly used in manufacturing and engineering to ensure that the object being tested can handle the additional weight without any harm or failure.

      Tamper Proof Packaging

      Tamper-proof packaging is designed to prevent tampering, either intentional or accidental, with the contents of the package. This type of packaging is often used to protect products from damage, spoilage, theft, and other forms of unauthorized access.
